                                                <div class="summarytext">
                                                    <div class="no-overflow"><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;">Õppeaine on arstiteaduse 5. kursuse üliõpilastele, mille&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(224, 62, 45); --darkreader-inline-color: var(--darkreader-text-e03e2d, #e24838);" data-darkreader-inline-color="">põhitähelepanu on pööratud kriitilises seisundis patsiendi käsitlusele.</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong>Õpiväljundid</strong></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;">Kursuse edukalt läbinud üliõpilane:</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -17.85pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; margin: 0cm 0cm 6.0pt 17.85pt;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">·<span style="font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->orienteerub erakorralise meditsiini süsteemis</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -17.85pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 18.0pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 6.0pt 17.85pt;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">·<span style="font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->teab patsientide triaaži põhimõtteid</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -17.85pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 18.0pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 6.0pt 17.85pt;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">·<span style="font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->tunneb ära kriitilises seisundis patsiendi</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -17.85pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 18.0pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 6.0pt 17.85pt;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">·<span style="font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->oskab käsitleda kriitilises seisundis patsienti ABCDE printsiibi alusel</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -17.85pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 18.0pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 6.0pt 17.85pt;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">·<span style="font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->oskab rakendada täiskasvanute elustamisvõtteid</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -17.85pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 18.0pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 6.0pt 17.85pt;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">·<span style="font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->tunneb ära eluohtlikud südamerütmihäireid ning teab nende ravi põhimõtteid</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -17.85pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 18.0pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 6.0pt 17.85pt;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">·<span style="font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->teab liittraumaga patsiendi esmase käsitluse põhimõtteid erakorralise meditsiini osakonnas</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -17.85pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 18.0pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 6.0pt 17.85pt;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">·<span style="font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->teab erakorralise kirurgilise patsiendi käsitluse põhimõtteid erakorralise meditsiini osakonnas</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -17.85pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 18.0pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 6.0pt 17.85pt;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">·<span style="font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->teab rindkerevaluga patsiendi käsitluse põhimõtteid erakorralise meditsiini osakonnas</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -17.85pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 18.0pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 6.0pt 17.85pt;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="line-height: 107%; font-family: Symbol;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">·<span style="font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: 'Times New Roman';">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]-->oskab koostada ja esitada haigusloost lühikokkuvõtte</span></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="mso-add-space: auto; text-indent: -17.85pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 18.0pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 6.0pt 17.85pt;"><br></p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="text-indent: -17.85pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 6pt 17.85pt; text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong>Õppetöö on jagatud kaheksaks alateemaks, mis koosnevad iseseisvast tööst ja praktikumist. Iga alateema on e-kursusel eraldi sektsioonis. </strong>Sealt leiate alateema õpiväljundid, omandatavad oskused ning õppematerjalid.&nbsp;</span></p>
<hr>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;"><strong>NB! Enne praktikumide algust tuleb läbida eelteadmiste test. Tulemusega alla 51% testi sooritanud üliõpilane praktikumis osaleda ei saa.</strong></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;">Praktikumid toimuvad L. Puusepa 8, anestesioloogia ja intensiivravi kliiniku õpperuumides (G1.2 203, G1.2 204, G1.1 214) ja&nbsp;simulatsioonikeskuses (B035, B038, B041). Iseseisev töö osakonnas toimub I, II ja III intensiivravi osakonnas (L. Puusepa 8, G1-korpus, II korrus).</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;">Täpne informatsioon vt jooksva semestri õppetöö korraldus, praktikumide plaan.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: medium;">Haiglas liikumiseks on vajalikud vahetusjalatsid ja arstikittel.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: rgb(52, 73, 94); font-size: medium; --darkreader-inline-color: var(--darkreader-text-34495e, #799ab5);" data-darkreader-inline-color=""><strong>Õppeaine arvestuse saamiseks peab üliõpilane osalema vähemalt seitsmes praktikumis, esitama arvestusel haigusjuhu kokkuvõtte ning sooritama edukalt meeskondliku simulatsioonülesande kriitilise seisundiga patsiendi käsitlemisel.</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 13.6000003814697px; line-height: 1.4;">Vajalik lisainformatsioon kliiniku sekretärilt (niina.fomina@ut.ee) L. Puusepa 8, G1.1 209, telefon 7318 405 või õppejõududelt.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: small;">Õppejõud: </span><span style="font-size: small;">prof J. Starkopf,&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: small;">T. Keskpaik (vastutav õppejõud) (triinu.keskpaik@ut.ee),&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: small;">K. Tamme,&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: small; text-align: initial;">P. Tähepõld, A. Sipria, </span><span style="font-size: small;">T. Laisaar, </span><span style="font-size: small;">O. Maasikas,&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: small;">V. Reinhard, </span><span style="font-size: small;">N. Vendt, M. Murrustem, </span><span style="font-size: small;">K. Kase, B. Sarana, </span><span style="font-size: small;">S. Poks</span></p></div>
